From: Sri Vidya Gunturi <sgunturi@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 12 May 2025 10:58:12 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 20/20] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL: hostapd: Define CONFIG_IEEE80211BE=y
 for wpasupplicant config in hwsim

Define CONFIG_IEEE80211BE=y for wpasupplicant config in hwsim for enabling
IEE80211BE specific features.

Signed-off-by: Sri Vidya Gunturi <sgunturi@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 tests/hwsim/example-wpa_supplicant.config | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/tests/hwsim/example-wpa_supplicant.config b/tests/hwsim/example-wpa_supplicant.config
index 59e3f85..b10be47 100644
--- a/tests/hwsim/example-wpa_supplicant.config
+++ b/tests/hwsim/example-wpa_supplicant.config
@@ -58,6 +58,7 @@ CONFIG_CTRL_IFACE_DBUS_INTRO=y
 CONFIG_IEEE80211R=y
 CONFIG_IEEE80211AC=y
 CONFIG_IEEE80211AX=y
+CONFIG_IEEE80211BE=y
 
 CONFIG_OCV=y
 
